                            <p>The graduates of the programmes are among the highly sought scientists in Nigerian research institutes (such as Nigerian Institute of Trypanosomiasis, Onchocerchiasis Research,  National Research Institute for Chemical Technology, Nigerian Institute of Leather and Science Technology, National Veterinary Research Institute, National Biotechnology Development Agency, etc.) and many private and international laboratories. </p>
